<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />手上的樹苗和種子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在市面上是買不到的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />雖然看起來不太精明，<delay8 />
但是只賣稀有物品喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是人不可貌相啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的灌木啊，<delay8 />跟一般的樹不同，<delay20 />
就算種在一起<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能夠正常地生長喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大量灌木<delay20 />一起開花的景象，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是非常漂亮啊，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />地球日<delay20 />可是為了提升<delay8 />人們對花草自然的重視<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而舉辦的重要活動喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你問我有沒有重視自然花草！？
<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然有啊！<delay frames="50" />像我今天早上就澆了很多水<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />呃！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那樣不對嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我平常都把花種在同一個地方照顧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果當中突然出現一朵我從沒看過的花。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後我把那朵花送給老媽，<delay20 />
沒想到她比我想像中的還要高興<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活中偶爾這樣也不錯，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你知道有什麼能改善島上環境的工作，<delay20 />
記得一定要告訴我喔？<delay frames="40" />
身為島上的居民，<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我很樂意幫忙！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就讓我們一起加油，<delay20 />讓這座島變得
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更棒更適合人居住吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>